dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Created an populated Admin 0 name and p-code fields 2. Created and populated reference name field 3. Admin 0 p-code appended to p-codes 4. Admin2 p-code for unit "Banadir" has been changed from "22" to "SO2201" to match format of other p-codes 5. As instructed by IMO, the admin 1 names in Admin2 have been replaced with the names from the Admin1 layer
